    'about.badge':'About Us','about.story.title':'Our Story','about.story.p1':'SERS started as a simple idea to make life easier for teachers in Saudi Arabia, providing modern digital tools that help them manage their educational records efficiently and professionally.','about.story.p2':'We believe education deserves the best tools, which is why we continuously develop innovative solutions that combine technology with outstanding educational content.','about.story.p3':'Today, SERS serves thousands of teachers through hundreds of educational templates and interactive services powered by artificial intelligence.',
